data.description: MLS# 273623 Charming one-story house with 3 bedrooms and 1 full bath. This home features an amazing open floor plan with a beautiful fireplace and hardwood floors throughout the home. There is a beautiful large island in the kitchen and a recent remodel in the back room. The home features a beautiful pet friendly backyard with an amazing gazebo that is perfect for entertaining your friends and family. This home has recently added a brand new roof, septic tank, and heating/cooling system. The home is located in a quiet neighborhood close to everything, so don't hesitate and schedule a showing today.
